Now, before the next bit, this bit is [b]VERY IMPORTANT[/b] as it is what creates the players-house area.

Okay, in client.java search for:

<blockquote>public boolean isInPitRoom() {</blockquote>

You should see some code a bit like this:

<blockquote>public boolean isInPitRoom() {
	if((absX >= 2394 && absX <= 2408 && absY >= 5168 && absY <=5175))
	return true;
	else
	return false;
	}</blockquote>

Now, underneath that put the following and make sure it is [b]exactly[/b] like the folllowing:

<blockquote>    public boolean isInShop()
    {
        return absX <= 2102 && absX >= 2084 && absY >= 3169 && absY <=3181;
    }</blockquote>

Okay, this will be explained later but it is basically the Workshop-where your player can train construction!!

